General.Name: Black Cat Syndicate Ltd
General.Description: Black Cat Syndicate Limited engages in the exploration and development of gold properties in Australia. It primarily holds interest in the Kal East gold project, which covers an area of 756 square kilometers located to the east of Kalgoorlie, Western Australia. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
